    "title": "Manabii wa Uongo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "manabii wa uongo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Biblia inaeleza kuhusu watu wengi waliodai kuwa manabii bila kuwa na mamlaka na wito wa kweli kutoka kwa Mungu. Walizungumza kana kwamba wanamwakilisha Mungu. Watu mara nyingi walipata ugumu kutofautisha kati ya manabii wa kweli na wa uongo. Manabii wa uongo kwa kawaida waliwaambia watu kile walichotaka kusikia (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:10-1Kgs22:14\">1 Wafalme 22:10–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:1-Jer28:4\">Yeremia 28:1–4</a>).</p><p>Kutokana na ugumu huu na kucheleweshwa kwa huruma kwa Bwana katika kuhukumu watu wake waasi, wengi walitilia shaka kama ujumbe wa Mungu kupitia manabii wake wa kweli ungetimia (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:19\">Isaya 5:19</a>). Wengine walikanusha kwamba chochote kingetokea wakati wa maisha yao. Je, adhabu ambayo mara nyingi imecheleweshwa ingeweza kusubiri kidogo zaidi?</p><p>Ezekieli alitabiri kwamba katika hukumu ijayo juu ya Yerusalemu, Mungu angeondoa manabii wa uongo. Hii ingewasaidia watu kutambua manabii wa kweli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:8-Ezek13:9\">Ezekieli 13:8–9</a>). Hukumu ya Mungu ingetokea bila kuchelewa—Bwana angekamilisha maneno yake hivi karibuni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:11\">13:11</a>). Kila mtu angejua ni maneno gani yalikuwa ya kweli kutoka kwa Mungu na ni maneno gani manabii wa uongo walifikiria.</p><p>Yesu alionya kwamba manabii wa uongo wangejitokeza siku za usoni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:11-Matt24:28\">Mathayo 24:11–28</a>). Wafuasi wake wa mwanzo walikutana na manabii wengi wa uongo (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:6-Acts13:12\">Matendo 13:6–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2 Petro 2:1–3</a>). Wakristo mara nyingi wanaweza kutambua manabii wa uongo kupitia mafundisho yao yasiyo sahihi kuhusu Kristo. Mafundisho haya yanaonyesha kwamba Roho wa Mungu hawaongozi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">1 Yohana 4:1–3</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:5\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 13:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:22\">18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:8-1Kgs22:28\">1 Wafalme 22:8–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13-Jer6:15\">Yeremia 6:13–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:13-Jer14:16\">14:13–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:1-Jer20:6\">20:1–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:1-Jer28:17\">28:1–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:21-Jer29:32\">29:21–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:6\">50:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:1-Ezek13:23\">Ezekieli 13:1–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:28\">22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:5\">Mika 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2 Wakorintho 11:13–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:3-2Tim4:4\">2 Timotheo 4:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2 Petro 2:1–3</a></p>",
